entry.title: Erdogan's Next Focus: Turkey's Place on the World Stage
entry.content: After seeing off his biggest election challenge, President Recep Tayyip Erdogan is turning his attention to fixing Turkey’s place on the map as an aspiring global power.

entry.title: Russia Follows Barrage on Kyiv With More Drone, Missile Attacks
entry.content: The strikes are part of an escalating campaign to degrade Ukraine’s air defenses and disrupt preparations for an offensive that Kyiv has signaled could be imminent.

entry.title: Russia Hits a Dead End in Bakhmut
entry.content: Victory in Bakhmut has given Russia something to show for its efforts after months without any meaningful gain, but its forces appear unable to capitalize on it.
